definitions.definition: The name of many places around the world.

subdefinitions.definition: A large number in the United States , including: A borough in Bergen County , New Jersey . A locality in Delran Township, Burlington County , New Jersey . A locality in Medford , Burlington County , New Jersey . A neighbourhood of Camden , Camden County , New Jersey . A locality in Washington Township, Gloucester County , New Jersey . A census-designated place in Middletown Township, Monmouth County , New Jersey . A city , the county seat of Major County , Oklahoma . A number of townships in the United States , listed under Fairview Township .

A number of places in Canada : A town in the Peace River Country of Alberta . A hamlet in Lethbridge County , southern Alberta . A neighbourhood in south-east Calgary , Alberta . A municipal district surrounding the town in northern Alberta ; in full, the Municipal District of Fairview No. 136 . A ghost town near Oliver , British Columbia . A neighbourhood in west Vancouver , British Columbia . A community in Halifax municipality, Nova Scotia . A community in Kenyon Township, North Glengarry , Ontario .
A number of places in the Philippines , including: A barangay of Baguio , Benguet , Philippines . A barangay of District V , Quezon City , Metro Manila , Philippines .
